videos.description: Jordan Bohannon's late 3-pointer is no good, but Keegan Murray stuns Penn State by tapping in the tying bucket for Iowa before the buzzer sounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Keegan Murray stuns Penn State Nittany Lions with buzzer-beater) 2022/02/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray taps in Bohannon's missed 3 at the buzzer to send game to OT

videos.description: Myles Dread hits a tying 3-pointer for Penn State late in overtime vs. Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Myles Dread hits the 3-pointer vs. Iowa Hawkeyes) 2022/02/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Myles Dread hits clutch, contested 3 to tie game late in OT
